sensed and perceived to be different from what they really are, showing examples of how the mind and the eyes can play tricks on each other. All you need is a piece of paper, a pencil and an eraser and you are ready to draw cool stuff. Once the drawing is complete, it can be colored, shaded or designed in any way you like to make it original.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFollowing these exercises is a great way to practice your craft and begin seeing things in terms of simple shapes within a complex object.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e&quot;,&quot;published_at&quot;:&quot;2025-02-03T13:31:33-05:00&quot;,&quot;created_at&quot;:&quot;2025-02-03T13:26:49-05:00&quot;,&quot;vendor&quot;:&quot;Catherine V. Holmes&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Art&quot;,&quot;tags&quot;:[&quot;Featured&quot;,&quot;New Release&quot;],&quot;price&quot;:1899,&quot;price_min&quot;:1899,&quot;price_max&quot;:1899,&quot;available&quot;:true,&quot;price_varies&quot;:false,&quot;compare_at_price&quot;:null,&quot;compare_at_price_min&quot;:0,&quot;compare_at_price_max&quot;:0,&quot;compare_at_price_varies&quot;:false,&quot;variants&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:51835823325552,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Default Title&quot;,&quot;option1&quot;:&quot;Default Title&quot;,&quot;option2&quot;:null,&quot;option3&quot;:null,&quot;sku&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;requires_shipping&quot;:true,&quot;taxable&quot;:false,&quot;featured_image&quot;:null,&quot;available&quot;:true,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;How to Draw Cool Stuff: Shading, Textures and Optical Illusion (2024 Edition)&quot;,&quot;public_title&quot;:null,&quot;options&quot;:[&quot;Default Title&quot;],&quot;price&quot;:1899,&quot;weight&quot;:408,&quot;compare_at_price&quot;:null,&quot;inventory_management&quot;:null,&quot;barcode&quot;:&quot;978-1956769739&quot;,&quot;requires_selling_plan&quot;:false,&quot;selling_plan_allocations&quot;:[],&quot;quantity_rule&quot;:{&quot;min&quot;:1,&quot;max&quot;:null,&quot;increment&quot;:1}}],&quot;images&quot