ond master’s degree at the University of Scranton.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\&quot;428\&quot; data-end=\&quot;855\&quot;\u003eHolmes specializes in portraiture, architectural artwork, and illustration. Her creations are deeply influenced by her emotions, thoughts, and experiences, drawing inspiration from nature, popular media, and human-made structures. She also finds creative motivation in her students’ interests and suggestions. In her own words, “Witnessing their success fuels my aspiration to elevate both my teaching and artistic creation.”\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\&quot;857\&quot; data-end=\&quot;1121\&quot;\u003eCatherine is a mother, an artist, an educator, and the author of the bestselling \u003cem data-start=\&quot;938\&quot; data-end=\&quot;962\&quot;\u003eHow to Draw Cool Stuff\u003c\/em\u003e series, \u003cem data-start=\&quot;971\&quot; data-end=\&quot;993\&quot;\u003eThe 15-Minute Artist\u003c\/em\u003e, and other popular drawing books. In addition to teaching in the classroom, she is also an online instructor for Craftsy.com.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e&quot;,&quot;published_at&quot;:&quot;2025-02-18T15:25:18-05:00&quot;,&quot;sort_order&quot;:&quot;manual&quot;,&quot;template_suffix&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;disjunctive&quot;:false,&quot;rules&quot;:[{&quot;column&quot;:&quot;vendor&quot;,&quot;relation&quot;:&quot;equals&quot;,&quot;condition&quot;:&quot;Catherine V. Holmes&quot;}],&quot;published_scope&quot;:&quot;global&quot;,&quot;image&quot;:{&quot;created_at&quot;:&quot;2025-02-20T12:11:23-05:00&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Catherine V. Holmes - Library Tales Publishing&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:700,&quot;height&quot;:700,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;\/\/librarytalespublishing.com\/cdn\/shop\/collections\/catherine-v-holmes-376852.jpg?v=1740071484&quot;}},{&quot;id&quot;:621461635440,&quot;handle&quot;:&quot;featured&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Featured&quot;,&quot;updated_at&quot;:&quot;